"1.. a wide patrol around a certain area. No one is to go beyond a certain 
point. NO ONE. Understood?"

"2ndly... I need the Autobot Whelljack-X. He supposely has something I want. 
Battera if you could get Wheeljack for me. Blackstorm... you can patrol." 

Soon enough she came to a hover & faced the 2 other fembots. "I want NO ONE 
to come further than this point.... in a radius. If anyone does slip by, 
inform me immediately! I will guarantee that they will be met with a very 
terminal surprize!" her crimson optics glowed. She was not kidding. This 
secret she had.. she wanted it hidden from the others. She would honestly be 
surprized if Rodimus didn't know this secret as well. 

--part1_149.10866411.2be896df_boundary
